item.title: Protobuf Extension
item.description: The Protobuf Extension # The protobuf extension is meanwhile a fix part of the specs and the spectools. In this, meanwhile built in, extesnion you define things for the protos. __proto extension in a type # The proto extension in a type defines the package, target file, imports (*.proto) and options __proto:package:authtargetfile:auth.protoimports:[]options:go_package:github.com/veith/doit-specs/dist/pb/auth;authpbjava_multiple_files:"true"java_outer_classname:AuthProtojava_package:com.furo.baseauth__proto extension in a field of a type # The proto extension in a field let you define the field id an can set a oneof group.
